These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: mango, grapes, watermelon
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, dancer, electrician
1. the person eating mango is in an even position##4
2. the police-officer is on the left or right of the electrician##3
3. the police-officer is the person eating grapes##1
4. the person eating watermelon is on the far left##1
5. the dancer is the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | watermelon | mango | grapes |
| Job    | dancer    | electrician | police-officer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, singing, traveling
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, van, train
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the van is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person driving the van is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | singing | traveling | baking |
| Transport   | train    | van     | motorbike        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, hiking, magic-tricks
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, rock, disco
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of funk##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks     | hiking | rock-climbing |
| Music-Genre   | rock | funk     | disco  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, family, time-travel
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, water-polo, climbing
1. the person watching family movies is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person watching family movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | family  | thriller  |
| Sport         | volleyball  | water-polo | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, writing, dancing
There are 3 different nationalities: american, thai, german
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is photography and the american##2
2. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
3. the german is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | photography   | dancing | writing    |
| Nationality   | thai | german     | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, video-games, reading
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, volleyball, snowboarding
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | video-games | reading | card-games   |
| Sport   | snowboarding     | biathlon    | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, superhero, satire
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, bird, guinea-pig
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
2. the person watching family movies is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person watching satire movies##2
3. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | family | superhero |
| Pet           | bird         | chinchilla         | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: lime, garlic, grapes
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, pony, goat
1. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the pony and the person eating lime##2
2. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | garlic | grapes | lime |
| Pet    | pony    | chinchilla | goat     |

