.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, house, metal
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, golf, baseball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the fan of house##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | house  | gospel  |
| Sport         | baseball | golf | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, tea
There 3 different types of food: tomato, pumpkin, asparagus
1. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person eating asparagus is in an even position##4
3. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | mirinda    | tea      | hot-chocolate |
| Food       | pumpkin | asparagus | tomato   |

