The people use 3 different means of transport: car, train, skateboard
1. the project-manager is on the right of the paramedic##1
2. the person driving the car is the engineer##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is the project-manager##1
4. the project-manager is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | paramedic | project-manager | engineer |
| Transport   | train | skateboard   | car |

