.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: american, nigerian, mexican
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, basketball, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the mexican##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is the nigerian##1
3. the mexican is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Nationality   | mexican  | american | nigerian   |
| Sport         | basketball | surfing   | rowing |

