.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, fishing, gardening
3 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, snake
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the owner of the ferret##2
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the ferret is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | fishing | gardening | traveling |
| Pet     | mouse    | snake  | ferret   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
