2. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of classical##1
3. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
4. the person watching drama movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire  | drama     | martial-arts |
