.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, iced-tea
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, russian, colombian
1. the colombian is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
2. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | 7up | sprite | iced-tea |
| Nationality   | russian   | colombian          | italian |

