.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: lizard, rat, horse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, tennis, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Pet     | rat  | horse   | lizard |
| Sport   | soccer | tennis | climbing       |

 